styleCard.description: An acoustic-driven, laid-back track evoking the scenic journey through Sarawak, blending contemporary indie folk with subtle traditional Malaysian elements, perfect for a contemplative road trip.

directions: Start at Sri Aman, Bahagian Sri Aman, Sarawak
Go northwest on Lorong 2 toward Lorong 1
Bear left to merge onto AH150 (01-27)
Take the exit on the left to merge onto the highway
At the traffic light, turn right on 6308A
At the roundabout, take the third exit onto 6308B
Take the exit on the left to merge onto the highway toward Pusat Bandar
At the roundabout, take the third exit onto Jalan Alan
Bear left to merge onto Jalan Salim
At the roundabout, take the second exit onto Jalan Bukit Lima
Finish at Jalan Kapor, Sibu, Bahagian Sibu, 96000, Sarawak, on the right

composition.style: AI generated music based on geographic and cultural context
